					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In order to have a working CPU, you would need the following:<br /><br />- ALU instructions<br />- immediate addressing<br />- indirect addressing<br />- condition flag manipulation<br />- branching<br />- interrupts<br />- subroutine calls and returns<br />- ability to have jump tables (make sure there is at least some way of doing this)<br /><br />Am I missing anything?</div>

